        <abstract>
            <p>CD and his family have come to the seashore, driven from home by scarlet fever at Down, death [of Charles Waring Darwin], and other family illness. Sorry to miss seeing JSH.</p>
            <p>Would be grateful to hear his objections to CD’s species speculations.</p>
        </abstract>
